snippet.title: Burnin' Rubber 5 Air - WHAT IS THAT?!
snippet.description:
► Burnin' Rubber 5 Air - WHAT IS THAT?! ◄

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Game: Burnin' Rubber 5 Air
 - Year: 2020
 - Developer: Xform
 - Publisher: AirConsole

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

As I promised you, I finally tried this game published on AirConsole.
In few words, is a copy of the original game with some minor changes, differend HUD, lowered graphic, etc.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

My Computer:
 - CPU: Intel Core i7-3770 3.40 GHz
 - GPU: Nvidia GeForce GTX 1070 8 GB
 - RAM: 16 GB
 - OS: Windows 10 | 64 bit
 - HDD: 1.5 TB

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Programs used:
 - Bandicam
 - VEGAS Pro 15.0
